0:00:00.300,0:00:01.060
Simama.

0:00:01.060,0:00:03.460
Hebu tuombe maombi haya

0:00:03.460,0:00:19.060
Mwombe Mungu akupe Neema ya kutokuwa mjinga wa imani yako  ukiwa katika shinikizo na majaribu

0:00:19.060,0:00:21.300
ya maradhi na magonjwa

0:00:21.300,0:00:22.520
Mwombe Mungu akupe Neema.

0:00:22.520,0:00:26.640
Nipe Neema Bwana, nisiwe mjinga wa imani yangu

0:00:26.640,0:00:41.760
Wakati wa shinikizo au mkandamizo wa majaribu ya maradhi, magonjwa, ugumu wa maisha na kutokufanikiwa

0:00:58.300,0:01:04.340
Chochote unachokabiliana nacho katika shinikizo hilo, mwombe Mungu, Bwana Yesu,

0:01:04.340,0:01:13.580
Nipe Neema ya kutokuwa mjinga wa imani yangu wakati wa shinikizo la majaribu ya hali yangu.

0:01:13.580,0:01:15.940
Hali yako ni nini?

0:01:15.940,0:01:22.100
Hali  hiyo inapojitokeza, inatufanya tunaonekana kusahau kuwa sisi ni Wakristo.

0:01:48.280,0:01:50.320
Kwa jina la Yesu Kristo.

0:01:50.320,0:01:51.200
[Amina.]

0:01:51.200,0:02:08.820
Unaonekana kusahau, unapokabiliwa na changamoto, hali, kwamba wewe upo jinsi Mungu anavyosema upo;

0:02:08.820,0:02:13.040
unaweza kufanya kile Mungu alichosema ufanye.

0:02:13.040,0:02:18.480
Unaonekana kusahau kwamba unacho kile Mungu alichosema unacho.

0:02:18.480,0:02:23.400
Wewe ukiwa Pamoja na Mungu, yote yawezekana

0:02:23.400,0:02:29.480
Unaonekana kusahau kwamba wakati wewe unakabiliwa na jambo.

0:02:32.420,0:02:35.440
Wewe na Mungu pamoja.

0:02:35.440,0:02:43.260
Unaonekana kusahau kwamba, wewe na Mungu mnaweza kuhamisha milima unapokabiliana na magumu.

0:02:43.260,0:02:45.720
lazima kuja pamoja, wewe na nani?

0:02:45.720,0:02:47.360
[Mungu.]

0:02:47.360,0:02:51.660
Wewe na Mungu lazima muwe pamoja, na kuunganisha mikono pamoja.

0:02:51.660,0:02:57.780
Hakuna mlima, na hakutakuwa na mlima.

0:02:57.780,0:03:04.900
Wewe na Mungu - lakini wanaonekana kusahau hii unapokabiliwa na nini?

0:03:04.900,0:03:06.680
Ugumu.

0:03:06.680,0:03:16.800
Unatakiwa kukumbuka nyakati ngumu zaidi na nyakati za kujaribu ulizokabiliana nazo huko nyuma.

0:03:16.800,0:03:25.260
ufunguo wa kufanikiwa katika maisha kama wewe ni mtoto wa Mungu - wakati wowote kuna ugumu

0:03:25.260,0:03:33.720
mara moja kukumbuka nyakati za majaribu zaidi na ugumu zilizokukabili huko nyuma.

0:03:33.720,0:03:43.080
Hii itakuapatia nguvu ya kukabiliana na ugumu unaokukabili sasa.

0:03:48.440,0:03:50.680
Yaani, tumia muda wako kukumbuka.

0:03:50.680,0:03:54.700
Hiki ndicho kilichotokea kwa Daudi.

0:03:54.700,0:03:59.500
Daudi alikwenda kwa kujiamini kwa kwa mfalme na akamwambia,

0:03:59.500,0:04:06.640
'Mfalme, ninakwenda kumkabili huyu Goliati  ambaye amewasumbua ndugu zangu na Nchi yangu

0:04:06.640,0:04:09.440
Mfalme akamtazama: "Wewe ni nani? '

0:04:09.440,0:04:16.920
Akamwambia, 'Nilitumia hii mikono yangu kumuua dubu'.

0:04:16.920,0:04:30.640
Mtu huyu alipokuja kusumbua Nchini mwao, mara moja alikumbuka nyakati ngumu na za majaribu alizoshinda.

0:04:30.640,0:04:38.780
Baada ya kumkumbuka dubu, akamuangalia Goliati na kusema, "hebu nikabiliane nae".

0:04:38.780,0:04:45.340
Kwa mfumo huo, hiyo ndiyo funguo kwako ya kushinda hali inayokukabili sasa.

0:04:45.340,0:04:51.620
Mwambie jirani yako "Hii ni funguo ya kushinda hali yangu ya sasa."

0:04:51.620,0:04:56.440
Unaweza kutumia ufunguo huo huo (mmoja) kufungua na kufunga.

0:04:56.440,0:05:03.260
Kumbuka kama Daudi alivyokumbuka, na alitembea kwa kujiamini kwenda kwa mfalme.

0:05:03.260,0:05:07.680
Tumia muda wako.

0:05:07.680,0:05:18.460
Wakati wowote unapokabiliana na changamoto au hali fulani, kumbuka hali ngumu zaidi na nyakati za majaribu

0:05:18.460,0:05:24.240
uliyokuwa nayo huko nyuma na ulishinda.

0:05:24.240,0:05:34.700
Hiyo itakuongezea nguvu ya kukabiliana na hali ya sasa.

0:05:34.700,0:05:42.220
Sijui ni kipi nitakabiliana nacho sasa ambacho kinaweza kuwa kikubwa kuliko kile nilichokabiliana nacho huko nyuma.

0:05:42.220,0:05:43.080
Unaona?

0:05:43.080,0:05:46.400
Kwa mfumo huo, sijui nini unaweza kabiliana nacho sasa

0:05:46.400,0:05:49.900
ambacho kinaweza kuwa zaidi ya kile ulichopitia huko nyuma.

0:05:49.900,0:05:57.140
Mara ukumbukapo hii, ambacho kitakuongezea nguvu ya kukabiliana na hali ya sasa.

0:05:57.140,0:06:05.340
Unakumbuka - nusu yetu hapa  tumetokea kijijini, kama sio 90% ya watu hapa.

0:06:05.340,0:06:10.840
Unapaswa kukumbuka siku hizo ulipokuwa unakunywa maji machafu.

0:06:10.840,0:06:19.400
Lakini leo unakunywa maji safi, na bado - homa ya manjano.

0:06:22.100,0:06:26.140
Sasa unakunywa maji safi.

0:06:26.140,0:06:30.200
Homa inatoka wapi?

0:06:30.200,0:06:33.340
Niambie.

0:06:33.340,0:06:36.920
Wewe, unatokea kijijini.

0:06:36.920,0:06:46.060
Kumbuka - katika siku hizo, ulipokuwa unapika supu, na uliendelea kuipasha kwa siku kumi.

0:06:46.060,0:06:50.720
Kadri unavyoipasha, ndivyo inavyozidi kuwa tamu.

0:06:57.280,0:07:00.140
Je, unaweza kupasha supu leo?

0:07:00.140,0:07:03.660
Ukipika supu leo, unaweza kuipasha kesho na kuila?

0:07:03.660,0:07:04.920
[Hapana]

0:07:04.920,0:07:07.380
Lakini kijijini ...

0:07:07.380,0:07:12.340
Haya ndio mambo ambayo yamekukuza.

0:07:12.340,0:07:15.160
Kumbuka jinsi ulivyozaliwa.

0:07:15.160,0:07:21.380
Wengi wenu hawakuzaliwa hospitalini.

0:07:21.380,0:07:27.840
Watu unaowaita maadui zako sasa, ndio waliokuwa wanakulisha ulipokuwa motto mchanga.

0:07:27.840,0:07:36.900
Mama yako peke yake asingeweza kukuhudumia peke yake - ulikuwa unaachwa ukitembea na kuzunguka kwao.

0:07:36.900,0:07:43.480
lakini leo unawaona kama ni watu wanaoweza kukuua..

0:07:43.480,0:07:46.840
Huu ndio ufunguo ninakupa leo.

0:07:46.840,0:07:58.640
Wakati wowote unapokabiliwa na changamoto ngumu, kumbuka changamoto na majaribu magumu zaidi ulipokuwa nayo zamani.

0:07:58.640,0:08:00.860
Hii itawajaza nini?

0:08:00.860,0:08:02.760
[Nguvu]

0:08:02.760,0:08:05.120
Katika nini?

0:08:05.120,0:08:07.020
Kukabiliana na nini?

0:08:07.020,0:08:09.440
Kukabiliana na  hali yako ya sasa.

0:08:09.440,0:08:11.820
Unahitaji nguvu.

0:08:17.320,0:08:19.740
Je unazungumzia kazi yako?

0:08:19.740,0:08:23.680
Kumbuka aina ya shule uliyosoma kijijini.

0:08:23.680,0:08:26.160
shule bila paa.

0:08:26.160,0:08:27.420
shule bila nini?

0:08:27.420,0:08:29.080
[Paa.]

0:08:29.080,0:08:38.120
Ulisoma huko chini ya mvua, chini ya jua - lakini angalia leo jinsi ulivyo.

0:08:38.120,0:08:43.980
Kama haujui aina ya shule uliyosoma kijijini siku hizo - rudi kijijini

0:08:43.980,0:08:49.500
na angalia ni wapi watoto wale wanapo somea leo.

0:08:49.500,0:08:52.140
Haya ni mambo unayaweka pamoja.

0:08:52.140,0:08:56.640
Ukifikiria kuhusu haya yote, utajua kwamba hakuna wa kukuzuia.

0:08:56.640,0:09:03.240
Sema, "Mimi mwenyewe ninaweza kujizuia; hakuna mwingine anayeweza kunizuia."

0:09:03.240,0:09:07.440
Hakuna mwingine anayeweza kukuzuia, unaweza kujizuia mwenyewe.

0:09:07.440,0:09:14.420
Kama hukuweza kuzuiwa wakati huo, sasa, hakuna anayeweza kukuzuia.

0:09:19.660,0:09:25.920
Unahitaji nguvu ili kuendelea zaidi.

0:09:25.920,0:09:30.740
Hivi ndivyo ninavyojilea mwenyewe.

0:09:30.740,0:09:42.100
Haijalishi ni kitu gani kinanijia, ninakaa chini na kuangalia matukio  yaliyotokea huko nilipotoka,

0:09:42.100,0:09:44.340
ambavyo nimepitia.

0:09:44.340,0:09:51.960
Chochote kinachotokea sasa, ninatabasamu na kusema, "Wewe ni motto mchanga."

0:09:55.520,0:09:57.600
Natabasamu.

0:09:57.600,0:10:07.740
Mara usipobadilishana  furaha yako na hali yako inayokukabili, unashinda

0:10:07.740,0:10:14.020
Mwambie jirani yako "Acha kubadilishana furaha yako na hali inayokukabili"

0:10:14.020,0:10:19.440
Mara ukiacha kubadilishana furaha na hali inayokukabili, daima utashinda

0:10:19.440,0:10:24.480
kwa sababu unahitaji furaha kushinda hali hiyo.

0:10:24.480,0:10:30.700
Haijalishi ukubwa wa hali hiyo, usipobadilishana furaha yako na hiyo hali, utaishinda.

0:10:30.700,0:10:34.740
Lakini mara furaha inapoondoka, huwezi kushinda hali hiyo.

0:10:34.740,0:10:37.540
Hiki ndicho kinacho kusudiwa kwenye hali hiyo  kuchukuliwa furaha yako.

0:10:37.540,0:10:39.940
Inataka kuchukua furaha yako.

0:10:39.940,0:10:41.200
Mungu wangu.

0:10:41.200,0:10:44.100
Inataka kukuona una huzuni.

0:10:44.100,0:10:45.900
Hali inataka kukuona na nini?

0:10:45.900,0:10:46.600
[huzuni.]

0:10:46.600,0:10:49.940
Inataka kukuona una huzuni.

0:10:49.940,0:10:53.280
Mara hali inapojitokeza, na unahuzunika.....

0:10:53.280,0:10:55.300
Jinsi gani nitalikabili hili?

0:10:55.300,0:10:56.760
Mungu wangu.

0:10:56.760,0:10:59.060
Hili ni kubwa mno kwangu.

0:10:59.060,0:11:02.320
Katika hali hiyo, huwezi kuomba.

0:11:02.320,0:11:05.500
Katika hali hiyo, huwezi kufikiri juu ya Mungu.

0:11:05.500,0:11:11.220
Katika hali hiyo ...

0:11:11.220,0:11:21.200
Mara moja utapoteza hali ya kufikiri, mtu yeyote anaye karibu anakuwa  adui yako.

0:11:21.200,0:11:24.440
Hautaweza kuonesha ubora wako.

0:11:24.440,0:11:33.360
Ninapokea simu: - Habari
- nyumba yako inaungua

0:11:33.360,0:11:39.440
- Una maana nyumba yangu?
- Ndiyo. Ni dhahiri. Zima moto wapo hapo.

0:11:39.440,0:11:42.600
Kabla ya hapo nilikuwa natabasamu.

0:11:49.700,0:11:53.480
Watu walio karibu wanauliza, "Ni nini kilichotokea sasa hivi?"

0:11:53.480,0:11:54.780
Nakuja.

0:11:54.780,0:11:58.540
Nimeuza kitu gani changu?

0:11:58.540,0:11:59.940
[Furaha.]

0:11:59.940,0:12:00.660
Na nini?

0:12:00.660,0:12:02.200
[Hali inayonikabili]

0:12:06.760,0:12:09.300
Jiangalie - Una furaha sasa.

0:12:09.300,0:12:13.320
Shetani anajua nini anaweza kufanya ili azuie furaha yako.

0:12:13.320,0:12:15.700
Anajua.

0:12:15.700,0:12:20.280
Kuna mtu anataka kukuona pale unapocheza.

0:12:20.280,0:12:22.080
Wapi?

0:12:22.080,0:12:23.400
Wanione.

0:12:25.400,0:12:26.700
Wapi?

0:12:29.620,0:12:34.040
Usifanye urahisi sana kwa shetani.

0:12:34.040,0:12:36.500
Kuna mtu anapambana na wewe.

0:12:36.500,0:12:43.040
Wewe unapumzika badala ya kukabiliana naye - unafanya urahisi tu.

0:12:43.040,0:12:47.560
Kuna mtu anataka kukuona pale unapocheza.

0:12:47.580,0:12:50.700
Wapi?

0:12:50.700,0:12:53.200
Sawa, huko. Nakuja.

0:12:53.200,0:12:56.440
Unataka kumalizia kucheza kwako.

0:12:56.440,0:12:58.820
Wangapi kati yenu wanaweza kufanya hivyo?

0:12:58.820,0:13:03.680
Umewahi kumalizia kucheza kabla ya kumsikiliza mtu ambaye alikuwa anataka kuonana na wewe?

0:13:03.680,0:13:06.880
Hapana, nina wajua nyinyi.

0:13:06.880,0:13:14.360
Hivyo tafadhali, acha kubadilishana furaha yako na  hali inayokukabili.

0:13:14.360,0:13:24.180
Kama una maumivu makali mkononi mwako, unaweza kuchagua kutobadilishana  maumivu hayo na furaha yako.

0:13:24.180,0:13:25.440
Habari gani?

0:13:25.440,0:13:26.540
Nzuri.

0:13:26.540,0:13:28.340
Najisikia  Maumivu yapo.

0:13:28.340,0:13:29.780
Vizuri.

0:13:29.780,0:13:32.080
Sijakuona muda.

0:13:32.080,0:13:33.520
Sikuwepo.

0:13:33.520,0:13:35.240
SAWA.

0:13:35.240,0:13:37.340
Maumivu bado yamo ndani yangu.

0:13:37.340,0:13:41.040
Maumivu hayataki kusikia furaha.

0:13:41.040,0:13:54.620
Pale ambapo pana maumivu na furaha ipo, maumivu hayatadumu.

0:13:54.620,0:14:01.760
Pale ambapo pana huzuni na furaha ipo, furaha haitadumu kabisa.

0:14:01.760,0:14:04.220
Haviwezi kuwa pamoja.

0:14:04.220,0:14:07.680
Ni kama paka na panya.

0:14:07.680,0:14:14.700
Ukichagua kuwa na furaha wakati wa kutafuta kazi, utapata mara moja.

0:14:18.100,0:14:29.980
Ukiwa unaumwa, unaweza kuchagua kuwa na furaha katika moyo wako - huo ugonjwa hautakaa muda mrefu.

0:14:29.980,0:14:36.480
Wakati ndoa yako ipo katika tishio, na kuna mtu anajaribu kuigeuza juu chini -

0:14:36.480,0:14:40.480
chagua kuwa na furaha, na angalia nini kitatokea baadaye.

0:14:40.480,0:14:47.020
Unajua kuwa ni hali ambayo inaikuta furaha; siyo furaha ambayo inaikuta hali.

0:14:47.020,0:14:54.740
Mwambie jirani yako, "Hali uikuta  furaha; furaha kamwe haikutani na hali hiyo."

0:14:54.740,0:14:59.420
Ukiyasoma maisha yako, ni hali ambayo uikuta  furaha.

0:14:59.420,0:15:04.840
Katika maisha ya mtu, hali inakuja kwa furaha.

0:15:04.840,0:15:10.760
Ni furaha ambayo inakumiliki wewe; Hali kamwe haikumiliki.

0:15:10.760,0:15:12.980
Hali uikuta  furaha.

0:15:12.980,0:15:15.720
Nyoka akiwa anakuja nyumbani kwako unafunga mlango.

0:15:15.720,0:15:20.600
Huwezi kukimbia na kuacha mlango wazi kwa ajili ya nyoka.

0:15:20.600,0:15:24.220
Acha kubadillishana furaha yako na nini?

0:15:24.220,0:15:25.880
[Hali inayokukabili.]

0:15:25.880,0:15:39.140
Ukiweza kufanya hivyo, hali itakuja lakini haitakaa na utajifunza somo kubwa ambalo litakusaidia.

0:15:44.300,0:15:48.260
Angalia matukio yaliyo nikuta tangu mwanzo.

0:15:48.260,0:15:52.340
Jina la taasisi hii halikutakiwa kuwa "Kanisa la Mataifa yote".

0:15:52.340,0:16:00.400
Wakati kanisa lina waumini 8 tu, Bwana alisema hili ni "Kanisa la Mataifa yote".

0:16:02.620,0:16:10.340
Taasisi ngapi unazijua nchini kwako ni "za Mataifa yote"?

0:16:13.780,0:16:19.740
Kama siyo taasisi ya maono na ujumbe maalum...

0:16:19.740,0:16:22.280
kanisa la kwanza liliharibiwa, la pili liliharibiwa.

0:16:22.280,0:16:27.600
Ni wangapi kati yenu bado mnafanya biashara mlizo anza nazo?

0:16:27.600,0:16:33.540
Sidhani kama kuna mtu hapa bado anafanya biashara, aliyoanza nayo mara ya kwanza kabisa katika maisha yake.

0:16:33.540,0:16:35.960
Baada ya changamoto nyingi ...

0:16:35.960,0:16:40.040
Kama haujui unakoelekea, huwezi kuendelea.

0:16:40.040,0:16:44.620
Hutaweza kusubiri kuachiliwa na Mungu kama haujui unapoelekea.

0:16:44.620,0:16:48.600
Ni wakati unapojua unakokwenda utasubiri kuachiliwa na Mungu.

0:16:48.600,0:16:55.080
Mwambie jirani yako, "Unapojua wapi unakwenda, utasubiri kuachiliwa na Mungu;

0:16:55.080,0:16:58.560
utasubiri kwa uvumilivu kuachiliwa na Mungu."

0:16:58.560,0:17:08.180
Lakini kama  hujui unakokwenda, utajiachilia mwenyewe.

0:17:11.240,0:17:13.720
Umekuwa ukijiachilia mwenyewe.

0:17:13.720,0:17:21.240
Unajiachilia mwenyewe katika biashara, katika ndoa, makanisani, kila mahali tu ...

0:17:21.240,0:17:22.700
Hii ni aibu......

0:17:22.700,0:17:24.440
Unawezaje kusema uongo dhidi yangu?

0:17:24.440,0:17:25.680
Unaondoka.

0:17:25.680,0:17:32.560
Unaondoka kwenye jamii, biashara, kanisa au ndoa.

0:17:32.560,0:17:34.220
Ni tusi la aina gani hili?

0:17:34.220,0:17:37.120
Hii ni aibu, Siamini kile unachosema.

0:17:37.120,0:17:40.720
Jinsi gani mchungaji huyu aseme uongo dhidi yangu?

0:17:40.720,0:17:44.840
Unaondoka kanisani.

0:17:44.840,0:17:49.320
Katika ndoa pia - mume wangu anasema uongo dhidi yangu!

0:17:49.320,0:17:51.260
Mke wangu anawezaje kunifanyia hivi.

0:17:51.260,0:17:54.600
Unaondoka kwenye ndoa.

0:17:54.600,0:17:56.780
Biashara - oh Mungu wangu.

0:17:56.780,0:17:58.480
Nilitakiwa nipande cheo.

0:17:58.480,0:18:01.160
Angalia walio chini yangu - nimemfundisha mtu huyu.

0:18:01.160,0:18:04.220
Mwangalie - amepandishwa cheo cha juu yangu.

0:18:04.220,0:18:07.400
Unaondoka kwenye biashara.

0:18:07.400,0:18:09.640
Haya ndio maisha ambayo umekuwa ukiishi.

0:18:09.640,0:18:11.560
Hali imekuwa ikikuachilia.

0:18:11.560,0:18:13.800
Changamoto zimekuwa zikikuachilia.

0:18:13.800,0:18:17.520
Ulimsikia Yusufu alichokisema alipokua kwenye shimo.

0:18:17.520,0:18:20.600
